{"tid":139990,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"安歷基比邊個趕走 不說了","createTime":"2017-03-02T00:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T06:51:27.000Z","uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d19812ccd125d45d41e9482cfeb0268cd7f37547","tid":139990,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:49:07.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿教練安歷基證實於季尾約滿後，將會離隊。<br />\n<br />\n自從巴塞隆拿於兩星期前歐聯以0:4受挫於巴黎聖日耳門後，有關主帥安歷基將不會留任的消息不絕於耳，當事人於球隊周三大勝希杭6:1後，證實季尾約滿後出「塞」，他說：「來季我不會是巴塞隆拿教練。」<br />\n<br />\n「這是困難、經計算及思索後得出來的決定，我認為要忠於自己所想。」這位前巴塞隊長在何3季，只贏得8個錦標，包括首季就率軍膺3冠王，而去季亦贏得西甲及西班牙國王盃。<br />\n<br />\n「面前尚有刺激的3個月，我們處於困難狀況，尤其在1個賽事，但在所有人同心協力下，如果眾星閃耀，我們是有機會平反敗局。」他續道：「在這3個月，我會貢獻自己的一切。」除了在歐聯處困境，巴塞現於西甲領先剛失分的皇家馬德里1分，但多踢1場。"},{"pid":"88d8de231d2e3fc3e8ee7b60639da2280e7d9148","tid":139990,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:50:56.000Z","msg":"雲加又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99869dc5691c21d5378aa4d9f170d67b2c77710a","tid":139990,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:51:13.000Z","msg":"又係小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba38553ffcf077524efcb9ed09ea53845cc4ecaf","tid":139990,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:51:59.000Z","msg":"只贏得8個錦標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0f40d3a02c053522ec8c8ae19087cc028382db","tid":139990,"uid":18669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只贏得8個錦標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292174fa6b55621a9e3c7b066e497dbaaf7e1827","tid":139990,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci